Package org.ejbca.core.model.approval

Class Approval

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ejbca.core.model.approval.Approval
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable, Comparable<Approval>
    public class Approval
extends Object
implements Comparable<Approval>, Externalizable
    Class representing an approval of a request. Includes information like: Approval admin certificate isApproved (rejected otherwise) ApprovalDate Comment Approvals are sorted by dates.
    Version:
